name: Les yeux de Marie
description:
In the last few weeks, I have been lucky enough to be able to take some shots of Ann Bernachin's work.

"In her works, sometimes, we no longer distinguish the artificial from the natural. It is in this moment of observation that one discovers a wonder of the nature which surrounds us.
The Between is also the link between two things, sometimes between two opposites, ambiguities or paradoxes. It is where we feel, where poetry arises, which gives rise to reflection on our relationship to the world, to life.
